dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents topography contours for Ozaukee County, Wisconsin in 2004. The original dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources in 2004.[The topographic (contour) mapping product covers the entire county and was prepared from 1"=800' negative scale black and white photography flown in the spring of 1994. The accuracy standard used is National Map Accuracy for 1" = 200' scale mapping. The contour files are non-overlapping, 3-D Microstation .dgn files and AutoCAD .dwg files are tiled by survey section.]
